{"tid":138949,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"堀北真希為守護家庭 宣佈引退　","createTime":"2017-03-01T04:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T16:00:55.000Z","uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"646b353d34afcb275070b4dedc9966c0e4097c3c","tid":138949,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"現年28歲嘅日本女星堀北真希前年閃嫁大自己12年嘅《同一屋簷下》男星山本耕史，去年12月生B成為人母，自嫁人後佢一直刻意減產，盛傳堀北將會效法山口百惠退出藝能界，專心做家庭主婦(新聞連結：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lUty2s￼&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lUty2s%EF%BF%BC%C2%A0&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=7d9f9e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lUty2s￼&nbsp;</a>)，昨晚堀北正式發表引退聲明，指為專心守護家庭，而退出藝能界。<br />\n<br />\n出道14年嘅堀北發表親筆聲明，內容指：「現在我已為人母，與家人每日過着幸福的日子，希望能全力守護着這份幸福。與山本討論過後，他尊重我的感受，從今我們二人會合力，組織充滿愛的家庭。」最後佢亦感謝一直支持自己嘅粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n14歲出道嘅堀北出道以來拍過《電車男》、《野豬大改造》與《花樣少年少女》等經典劇集，但佢婚後刻意減產，推掉廣告合約，更將影迷會關閉，早已傳出有引退念頭。"},{"pid":"cd3008501f839d3b4900b07864e51ce5350cd85e","tid":138949,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b98c6063dcf5c02d5b5531c86c81e8fe5f45d4","tid":138949,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e6194380e68ff0ea8aa250b6be42c52c2c7f8a","tid":138949,"uid":16472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"Av女優？"},{"pid":"2ecc5fa5e60315286b189c1b5a81b30adb3cde25","tid":138949,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:00:55.000Z","msg":"好靚呀真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}